text: Tamás Sors is a Hungarian Paralympic swimmer who competes in S9 classification events. He has won Paralympics gold twice in the 100m butterfly at Beijing and London. ==References== Category:Hungarian male swimmers Category:Swimmers at the 2008 Summer Paralympics Category:Swimmers at the 2012 Summer Paralympics Category:Paralympic gold medalists for Hungary Category:Paralympic silver medalists for Hungary Category:Paralympic bronze medalists for Hungary Category:Living people Category:1991 births Category:Medalists at the 2008 Summer Paralympics Category:Medalists at the 2012 Summer Paralympics Category:S9-classified Paralympic swimmers Category:Sportspeople from Pécs Category:Medalists at the 2016 Summer Paralympics Category:Medalists at the World Para Swimming Championships Category:Medalists at the World Para Swimming European Championships Category:Paralympic medalists in swimming Category:Paralympic swimmers of Hungary
